'''Abduvohid Nematov''' (born 20 March 2001) is an Uzbek professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays as a goalkeeper for [[FC Nasaf|Nasaf]] and the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan national team]].

==Career==
===International===
Nematov made his debut for the [[Uzbekistan national football team|Uzbekistan]] main team on 3 September 2020 in a [[Friendly (sport)|Friendly]] match against [[Tajikistan national football team|Tajikistan]].<ref>[https://www.national-football-teams.com/matches/report/27778/Uzbekistan_Tajikistan.html Uzbekistan 2–1 Tajikistan]</ref>

